reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 25, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Not very effective.
reviews.reviewText: I was hoping that these would help to replace some of the broken edges of my dustpans, but when I attached the things they did not help. Rather, when we used them the effective result was that they actually grabbed less than before and left weird dirt streaks at the end. I would not recommend these generally as a result.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 23, 2023
reviews.reviewText: These were easy to put on and work well for creating a "seal" with the floor. My only problem, and it's my own fault for not measuring, is that my dustpan is too wide by a couple of inches on each side. But I haven't had any trouble just sweeping up the center. With four pieces available, I may just cut one in half and slide it on. I like that I can replace the lip on the dustpan and save having to replace the whole thing!
